title: SHINee - Everybody (2013)
description:
"Everybody is the fifth EP recorded and performed by the South Korean contemporary R&B idol group Shinee. It has been released for physical purchase domestically and for digital download globally on October 14, 2013. The EP was produced by the record label of S.M. Entertainment and distributed by KMP Holdings. The tracks "Everybody" and "Symptoms" were chosen as the lead singles for the promotional cycle."
(Wikipedia)
